# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# E83 Pickleball — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env.local for local development. Never commit .env.local to git.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── App URL ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Must be the full public URL of your deployment.
# Vercel sets this automatically as VERCEL_URL — set your custom domain here.
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

# ─── Turso Database ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for production (Vercel). Leave empty for local dev — falls back to
# a local SQLite file at .data/local.db automatically.
#
# Setup:
#   1. Go to https://app.turso.tech and create a free account
#   2. Create a new database (choose Singapore region for best latency from VN)
#   3. Click "Connect" → copy the URL and token below
#
TURSO_DB_URL=libsql://your-db-name.turso.io
TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=your-turso-auth-token

# ─── Gmail SMTP ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NOT needed here — Gmail credentials are saved via Admin Settings UI and
# stored in the Turso database. This comment is just for reference.
#
# To configure email:
#   1. Deploy the app
#   2. Go to /admin → Settings → Cấu hình Email
#   3. Enter your Gmail address + 16-char App Password
#   4. Click "Lưu cấu hình email"
#   5. Test with the built-in test email button
